data.description:
St Lucie West Lake Charles community features the beautiful St James open floorplan moving ready home with 2 bedrooms, two bathrooms, plus Den or a 3rd bedroom. Property offers tranquil private preserve views. The kitchen counters, white cabinets, large kitchen sink, and new microwave all have been replaced in 2023. Rest easy knowing the air conditioning unit was replaced in 2013, and the water heater in 2020. Master bathroom with shower & roman tub, new shower tile and cabinets. Master bedroom offers a walk-in closet plus additional closet.  Second bathroom new wall tile & cabinets. Spacious family room open floor plan with a blend of comfort and style, including flexible dining area, and casual kitchen breakfast nook overlooking the private preserve. The outdoor living and back patio overlook a backdrop of trees, offering a private oasis for relaxation. Additional upgrades plantation shutters, rain gutters, and the home is equipped with hurricane accordion shutters. 

Lake Charles is a 24/7 manned gated community located in the heart of the master planned community of St Lucie West with over 500 acres of open nature preserve and inter-connecting lakes. The community offers a beautiful clubhouse with many activities and residents clubs year-round, including lighted tennis courts, basketball, jogging, biking, shuffleboard, playground, picnic area, volleyball, bocce court. Lake Charles reasonable HOA Fee includes lawn care, gate security service, turf and shrubs fertilization four times a year, and Comcast basic cable TV, internet. Two pets per household permitted.
